OOC: Haven't seen her in a while, have you? ;)

Bic:

Meteara looked up to the sky. She felt something.

Meteara: Yet again. The Cybertronians will never learn...

She brought up a holographic display of the battle at the Maximal 
base. She was not happy about it, but she felt confident the battle 
would not damage the sphere buried in the mountains to the west.

Meteara: This needs monitoring. I might have to intervene...
